<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bid Update - IpTruck</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f39c12;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .info-badge {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            color: #6c5700;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .booking-details {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .motivation-section {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üìã Bid Update</h1>
        <p>Information about your submitted bid</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="info-badge">
            <h2>Bid Status Update</h2>
            <p>Your bid for booking <strong>#<%= bookingId %></strong> was not selected this time.</p>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Hello <%= carrierCompany %>,</h2>
        
        <p>Thank you for your interest in booking <strong>#<%= bookingId %></strong>. We appreciate the time and effort you put into submitting your bid.</p>
        
        <div class="booking-details">
            <p><strong>Bid ID:</strong> <%= bidId %></p>
            <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> <%= bookingId %></p>
            <p><strong>Contact Person:</strong> <%= contactPerson %></p>
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= reason %></p>
        
        <div class="motivation-section">
            <h3>üöÄ Don't Give Up!</h3>
            <p>While this bid wasn't selected, there are many more opportunities available on IpTruck. Here's what you can do:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>üìã Browse new bookings that match your capabilities</li>
                <li>‚≠ê Build your reputation with successful deliveries</li>
                <li>üí∞ Adjust your pricing strategy based on market trends</li>
                <li>üöõ Ensure your truck information is up-to-date</li>
                <li>üì± Enable notifications for bookings in your area</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <center>
            <a href="https://iptruck.com/dashboard" class="button">Find New Bookings</a>
        </center>
        
        <p><strong>üí° Tips for Future Bids:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Submit competitive pricing while maintaining profitability</li>
            <li>Provide detailed truck and driver information</li>
            <li>Respond quickly to new booking notifications</li>
            <li>Include a personalized message highlighting your strengths</li>
            <li>Maintain a good rating and positive reviews</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>Need Support?</strong></p>
        <p>If you have questions about improving your bid success rate or need assistance with the platform, our team is here to help. Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@iptruck.com">support@iptruck.com</a></p>
        
        <p>Thank you for being part of the IpTruck community. We look forward to helping you secure your next booking!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The IpTruck Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>¬© 2024 IpTruck. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>You received this email because of a bid status update.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
